as.leap

Class LCGeoPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • as.leap.LCGeoPoint

  • public class LCGeoPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    LCGeoPoint represents a latitude / longitude point that may be associated with a key in a LCObject or used as a reference point for geo queries. This allows proximity based queries on the key.
